== ''The Addams Family: Mansion Mayhem'' ==
'''''The Addams Family: Mansion Mayhem''''' is a 3D platforming adventure game released on September 24, 2021 for the [[PlayStation 4]], [[Nintendo Switch]], PC, and [[Xbox One]]/[[Xbox Series X and Series S|Series X and S]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=Addams Family: Mansion Mayhem Outright Games - |url=https://outrightgames.com/us/games/the-addams-family-mansion-mayhem/ |access-date=2022-09-21 |website=Outright Games |language=en-US}}</ref> It was developed by PHL Collective and published by Outright Games. The game's art and assets are based on 2019's ''[[The Addams Family (2019 film)|The Addams Family]]'' and 2021's ''[[The Addams Family 2]]'' films.

